13:02.581 --> 13:03.849
- So...
- Do what he says.

13:03.916 --> 13:05.184
- Do what Bentley says?
- Yeah.

13:05.251 --> 13:08.254
- He can't give me orders.

13:08.320 --> 13:10.890
- Well, happy birthday.
- Thank you.

13:10.956 --> 13:14.927
- Enjoy the rest of your day.
- I will.

13:14.994 --> 13:16.095
See you later.
- Let me know

13:16.162 --> 13:17.296
how the rest
of your night goes.

13:17.363 --> 13:18.397
- Bye.

13:18.464 --> 13:22.434
