13:22.501 --> 13:23.903
{\an8}<i>- We called Dr. Drew,</i>

13:23.969 --> 13:25.204
{\an8}<i>and he agreed</i>
<i>to have us on his show</i>

13:25.271 --> 13:27.306
{\an8}<i>to speak out</i>
<i>about all the rumors.</i>

13:28.974 --> 13:31.043
{\an8}- You excited for LA?
- Yeah.

13:31.110 --> 13:33.012
{\an1}- This is stupid.
You know what I'm excited for?

13:33.078 --> 13:35.247
- Hmm?
- The tacos.

13:35.314 --> 13:37.850
{\an1}I'm sorry, the food's
just better in LA.

13:37.917 --> 13:39.585
- Mm-hmm.
- That's just how it is.

13:39.652 --> 13:42.288
[cell phone ringing]

13:44.356 --> 13:45.591
{\an8}Hey.

13:45.658 --> 13:47.393
{\an8}<i>- Hey, what's up?</i>
- How are you?

13:49.461 --> 13:50.429
{\an8}- What's the matter?

14:02.474 --> 14:04.276
{\an8}- Well, how can we help?

14:07.279 --> 14:09.215
- We're actually flying to LA.

14:09.281 --> 14:10.616
{\an1}We're going on
the Dr. Drew show,

14:10.683 --> 14:15.187
{\an1}so if you feel like you need
to get away for a while,

14:15.254 --> 14:17.890
if I get you a ticket, you know,

14:17.957 --> 14:19.325
{\an1}you can come out and stay
for a couple days.

14:19.391 --> 14:21.093
{\an1}We can figure out
what's going on with you

14:21.160 --> 14:23.062
and see how we can help.

14:26.065 --> 14:27.433
{\an8}- All right, you know what?

14:27.499 --> 14:29.368
{\an7}I'm gonna go ahead
and book the flight right now.

14:29.435 --> 14:31.403
{\an8}<i>- All right, sounds good.</i>
- All right, bye.

14:33.138 --> 14:35.207
{\an8}That was my son, Christopher.

14:35.274 --> 14:38.477
{\an8}- Christopher is...?
- He is 25.

14:38.544 --> 14:41.247
