18:55.567 --> 18:57.369
{\an1}We don't need two people
doing the same thing,

18:57.436 --> 18:59.438
{\an1}so if you want,
you can do the fruit.

18:59.505 --> 19:02.241
{\an1}I'm gonna take care
of this for you, okay?

19:02.307 --> 19:03.475
Thank you.

19:09.214 --> 19:11.717
So this cuts up them very well.

19:21.827 --> 19:24.396
So, Kiana, the reason
why I gave these to you--

19:24.463 --> 19:25.864
that is actually
the quicker way.

19:25.931 --> 19:28.300
{\an3}That's why they make those,
so that this will go by

19:28.367 --> 19:29.668
so much quicker than this,

19:29.735 --> 19:31.336
{\an3}so it's easier
for everyone's hands,

19:31.403 --> 19:32.671
everything like that.

19:32.738 --> 19:35.407
{\an3}So you have about ten minutes
until we open.

19:35.474 --> 19:37.543
{\an3}This trash has to be out,
and you--

19:37.609 --> 19:39.678
{\an3}I still have to talk to you
about the other night

19:39.745 --> 19:42.681
{\an3}because it's not appropriate
or professional

19:42.748 --> 19:44.917
{\an3}to keep continuing on
without talking about things,

19:44.983 --> 19:45.918
so I just wanted to let you

19:45.984 --> 19:47.386
know that, okay?
- Okay.

19:47.452 --> 19:49.821
{\an3}- So I'm letting you know
the time.

19:49.888 --> 19:55.427
<i>♪ ♪</i>

19:55.494 --> 19:58.597
<i>[clock ticking]</i>

20:02.467 --> 20:05.404
{\an8}<i>[upbeat music]</i>

20:05.470 --> 20:08.206
- Come here, hurry.
