20:10.342 --> 20:11.910
Hi, Jayde-Jayde.

20:11.977 --> 20:14.546
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:14.613 --> 20:16.782
{\an8}Can you say, "Happy birthday"?

20:22.421 --> 20:23.755
{\an8}Surprise!

20:23.822 --> 20:26.391
{\an8}- Hi.
