20:26.458 --> 20:29.528
{\an8}- Mama!
- Happy birthday.

20:29.595 --> 20:30.929
{\an9}- Hi.

20:34.499 --> 20:36.602
{\an8}Give me a kiss, Benny.
Thank you.

20:36.668 --> 20:38.670
{\an8}<i>- ♪ Da-da, da-da, da-da ♪</i>

20:38.737 --> 20:39.972
{\an8}<i>♪ Da-da, da-da ♪</i>
