20:40.038 --> 20:41.907
{\an1}- Now you got to blow out
your candles

20:41.974 --> 20:44.710
so we don't burn the house down.

20:44.776 --> 20:45.944
- You want to blow them out?

20:46.011 --> 20:47.846
{\an3}Hold on, we can eat them
in just a second.

20:47.913 --> 20:49.348
{\an3}Ready?

20:49.414 --> 20:52.017
[baby exclaiming]

20:52.084 --> 20:54.019
{\an3}- Yay.

20:55.454 --> 20:56.722
Thanks, guys.

20:56.788 --> 20:57.823
- You're welcome.
- You're welcome.

20:57.889 --> 21:00.626
- Were you surprised?
- Yes.

21:00.692 --> 21:02.961
