21:03.028 --> 21:04.129
I was confused.

21:04.196 --> 21:07.399
{\an1}- Well, it was like trying
to organize a circus act, but...

21:07.466 --> 21:10.802
- Well, that's how our pretty
much everyday life is, so...

21:10.869 --> 21:12.604
- And I was the ringmaster.

21:12.671 --> 21:17.442
{\an1}Jayde's the bearded lady 'cause
she's got a cupcake beard.

21:17.509 --> 21:19.544
Happy birthday.

21:19.611 --> 21:21.513
- Thank you very much.

21:21.580 --> 21:23.548
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21:23.615 --> 21:26.284
<i>- What a day.</i>
<i>- Yup.</i>

21:26.351 --> 21:28.053
{\an3}- Did you enjoy
your birthday, though?

21:28.120 --> 21:29.721
- Yeah, I did.

21:29.788 --> 21:32.858
So what's the plan for tomorrow?

21:32.924 --> 21:36.795
{\an1}'Cause Bentley
is starting second grade.

21:36.862 --> 21:38.730
{\an1}I mean, he can pretty much
get himself ready,

21:38.797 --> 21:41.633
{\an1}and we'll just
get the babies dressed.

21:41.700 --> 21:44.503
{\an1}So do you think
Ryan's gonna be there?

21:44.569 --> 21:46.605
- No, I don't.

21:46.672 --> 21:49.708
- He probably doesn't even know
that tomorrow's his first day.

21:49.775 --> 21:50.909
{\an8}- You know, last time
I was here,

21:50.976 --> 21:52.678
{\an8}Bentley went and stayed
at Ryan's place,

21:52.744 --> 21:54.780
{\an8}and that seemed
like it went well.

21:54.846 --> 21:57.516
{\an3}Have--like, have you heard
from Ryan since then?

21:57.582 --> 22:01.753
- Nope, and I hadn't heard from
him for two months before then.

22:02.988 --> 22:06.992
{\an1}I literally only hear from him
or see him if we're filming.

22:09.161 --> 22:10.829
{\an1}It's true.

22:10.896 --> 22:14.399
<i>[soft music]</i>

22:14.466 --> 22:16.902
{\an1}I'm not expecting
Ryan to be there tomorrow.

22:16.968 --> 22:19.604
{\an1}I don't expect to hear from him
or anything,

22:19.671 --> 22:22.407
because we never do.

22:22.474 --> 22:24.576
{\an3}- If he's there, he's there.
If he's not, he's not.

22:24.643 --> 22:25.811
{\an1}- Right.

22:25.877 --> 22:30.816
<i>♪ ♪</i>

22:30.882 --> 22:33.719
{\an8}<i>[upbeat music]</i>

22:33.785 --> 22:35.887
{\an8}<i>- We're in LA,</i>
<i>and I'm meeting Matt's son</i>

22:35.954 --> 22:38.023
{\an8}<i>for the first time.</i>

22:38.090 --> 22:41.626
{\an8}- Hey.
- How's it going?

22:41.693 --> 22:44.062
{\an8}- How you doing, man?
- Good. Long time no see.

22:44.129 --> 22:46.698
- Yeah. This is Amber.
- Hi.

22:46.765 --> 22:49.601
- Hi, nice to meet you.
I'm Chris.

22:49.668 --> 22:51.703
Very cool, very cool.
- Oh, you're so tall.

22:51.770 --> 22:52.704
- I'm a fan of you guys.

22:52.771 --> 22:54.506
Awesome.
- Oh, thank you.

22:54.573 --> 22:56.875
<i>We're getting ready to go</i>
<i>on the Dr. Drew show today,</i>

22:56.942 --> 22:59.044
<i>and I'm feeling</i>
<i>a little nervous.</i>

22:59.111 --> 23:01.847
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23:01.913 --> 23:03.715
- When I was coming,
were you expecting,

23:03.782 --> 23:05.083
{\an1}like, somebody completely
different?

23:05.150 --> 23:06.852
{\an8}Like--like, just--
- Different how?

23:06.918 --> 23:08.720
{\an7}- Like, a total
just strung-out--

23:08.787 --> 23:10.055
{\an3}- No, I didn't expect--
I didn't expect that.

23:10.122 --> 23:11.389
- No.
- Oh, okay, cool.

23:11.456 --> 23:12.758
- He was just--
the main thing

23:12.824 --> 23:14.526
{\an3}that was going on with him
was he was so nervous

23:14.593 --> 23:16.461
to see you after so long.
- Yeah?

23:16.528 --> 23:18.997
{\an3}- He didn't really know
how you were gonna react.

23:19.064 --> 23:21.032
{\an1}- I think people think too much
into the situation, like,

23:21.099 --> 23:22.734
when it comes to me and you.

23:22.801 --> 23:24.136
- And I think that there's a lot
of people out there--

23:24.202 --> 23:25.637
{\an1}- You were never--
you were never awful at all.

23:25.704 --> 23:27.606
- No, no.
- Not even once.

23:27.672 --> 23:29.708
{\an3}- You couldn't have came at
a better time, honestly,

23:29.775 --> 23:31.743
{\an3}'cause this is exactly
why we're here.

23:31.810 --> 23:34.513
{\an3}You know, anybody can contact
the media these days

23:34.579 --> 23:37.482
and say whatever the hell
they want, you know, and--

23:37.549 --> 23:38.884
{\an3}well, you've gotten
a taste of that.

23:38.950 --> 23:40.051
- Yeah, I have.
- And...

23:40.118 --> 23:41.653
- Yeah, thanks for that,
by the way.

